萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter) 觉得她“根本不知道”公众是否会喜欢“浓缩咖啡” https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-felt-she-had-literally-no-idea-if-the-public-would-like-espresso-3825392?u tm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=sabrina-carpenter-fet-she-have-literally-no-idea-if-the-public-would-like-espressoDaniel Peters Tue, 31 Dec 2024 07:55:39 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3825392 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我喜欢它，那一刻对我来说这就是最重要的”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-felt-she-had-literally-no-idea-if-the-public-would-like-espresso-3825392">萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter) 认为她“根本不知道”公众是否会喜欢《Espresso》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter)</a>讨论了她 2024 年的热门单曲《Espresso》，并透露，在该单曲发行后，她觉得自己“根本不知道”公众是否会喜欢它。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-songs-2024-3817596">2024 年 50 首最佳歌曲</a></strong></li></ul><p>就在昨天（12 月 30 日），Carpenter 推出了与 Dunkin Donuts 的合作—— <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-teams-up-with-dunkin-for-shakin-espresso-signature-drink-3825346">推出一款新的招牌咖啡——Sabrina&#39;s Brown Sugar Shakin&#39; Espresso</a> 。这是 Carpenter 和单曲《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sabrina-carpenter-short-n-sweet-review-3787293">Short n&#39; Sweet</a> 》成功一年的众多成果之一。</p><p>然而，它的成功是卡彭特完全没有预料到的，他在接受<a href="https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/music-news/sabrina-carpenter-dunkin-collab-espresso-new-music-1236095371/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《好莱坞报道》的</em></a>新采访时谈到了这一点。</p><p> “我记得决定在夏初推出这首歌，并认为浓缩咖啡更像是一种秋季饮料，”她说。</p><p> “我真的不知道它是否会产生联系，但这首歌的情感和声音以及它所带来的信心是我真正相信的。”</p><p>她继续说道：“所以我真的不知道有人会喜欢它，但我喜欢它，这就是那一刻对我来说最重要的事情，也是我一遍又一遍地记住的事情。”</p><p> 《Espresso》于 4 月份发行，先于 8 月份的《Short n&#39; Sweet》发行。它在英国单曲排行榜上名列前茅，并被提名为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-nominations-2025-check-out-the-full-list-of-nominations-here-3811039">年度唱片和格莱美奖最佳流行独奏表演。</a></p><p>另一方面， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-sabrina-carpenter-make-her-debut-on-nprs-tiny-desk-3824246">Carpenter 最近在 NPR 的<i>Tiny Desk</i>系列节目中首次亮相</a>，而她的歌曲“Bed Chem”被评为<a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-songs-2024"><i>NME</i> 2024 年 50 首最佳歌曲</a>之一。 </p><figure id="attachment_3819496" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3819496" style="width: 1200px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3819496" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/42-SABRINA-CARPENTER@1200x1200.jpg" alt="Sabrina Carpenter Short N Sweet 专辑封面，Island Records 摄" width="1200" height="1200" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/42-SABRINA-CARPENTER@1200x1200.jpg 1200w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/42-SABRINA-CARPENTER@1200x1200-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/42-SABRINA-CARPENTER@1200x1200-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/42-SABRINA-CARPENTER@1200x1200-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/42-SABRINA-CARPENTER@1200x1200-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/42-SABRINA-CARPENTER@1200x1200-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3819496" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：岛屿唱片公司</figcaption></figure><p>Carpenter 将于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-announces-uk-and-european-tour-for-2025-buy-tickets-3776153">明年将“Short N&#39; Sweet”巡演带到英国</a>，日期包括明年夏天<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-announced-as-bst-hyde-park-2025-headliner-3819535">在 BST 海德公园举行的大型头条节目</a>。 <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fsabrina-carpenter-tickets%2Fartist%2F2001092" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处获取门票</a>。</p><p> 2025 年，她还将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/CHAPPELL-ROAN">Chappell Roan</a>一起在<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/primavera-sound-festival">Primavera Sound 上</a>亮相，并开始她的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-announces-uk-and-european-tour-for-2025-buy-tickets-3776153">英国和欧洲巡演</a>，巡演将于明年举行，前<a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/rachel-chinouriri-15-01-2024-3570580"><i>NME</i>封面</a>明星<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rachel-chinouriri">Rachel Chinouriri</a>将作为特邀嘉宾。</p><p>这些演出将于 3 月 3 日在都柏林 3Arena 拉开帷幕，随后还将在伯明翰、伦敦和曼彻斯特举办更多演出 - 请参阅下面的所有日期并<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/sabrina-carpenter-tickets/artist/2001092?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=wr6WK%3A2K9xyKR7zUPb3vE3Q-UkCUhdxsCzkYRk0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>抢票。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-felt-she-had-literally-no-idea-if-the-public-would-like-espresso-3825392">萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter) 认为她“根本不知道”公众是否会喜欢《Espresso》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
